# Events: Bring Your Community Together

Thoughtfully designed event management that connects with how your community actually communicates. Whether you're organizing a local meeting, a virtual workshop, or a regional gathering, Belcoda's event tools help you reach people, track participation, and stay connected—without the complexity.

## Overview

Belcoda Events bridges the gap between digital organizing and real-world connection. Create event pages that work across channels, send automated communications that arrive when they matter, and track participation in ways that enrich your community understanding—not just fill spreadsheets.

The system recognizes that different communities communicate differently. Some prefer email, others WhatsApp. Some need detailed registration forms, others want frictionless signup via QR code. Belcoda adapts to your community's communication patterns rather than forcing them to adapt to your tools.

---

## Event Pages That Welcome Everyone

### Beautiful, Accessible Public Pages

Each event gets its own clean, mobile-optimized page that puts the important details front and center: what's happening, when, where, and how to join. Feature images draw attention. Descriptions can include rich formatting for context and instructions. Address information renders clearly, and virtual meeting links are automatically detected and displayed with platform logos.

Signup forms collect exactly what you need—nothing more. Choose from standard fields like address, date of birth, and organization, or create custom fields specific to your event. Ask dietary preferences for a community meal. Collect skill levels for a workshop. Gather accessibility needs for an in-person gathering. Every field can be marked as optional or required, giving you flexibility without overwhelming participants.

The system handles capacity elegantly. Set a maximum number of signups, and the counter updates in real-time, creating gentle urgency without pressure. When someone signs up, they're immediately recognized if they're already in your community database—no need to re-enter information they've provided before.

### Instant Calendar Integration

One-click calendar export means your event appears in people's personal calendars. Timezone support ensures everyone knows when to show up, regardless of where they're located. The "Add to Calendar" button works with all major calendar applications, reducing the mental overhead of remembering event details.

---

## WhatsApp Integration: Meet People Where They Are

### QR Code Signup

For communities that live on WhatsApp, event registration doesn't need to mean filling out web forms. Generate a WhatsApp QR code that people can scan at meetings, print on flyers, or share in group chats. One scan opens WhatsApp with your event information pre-filled, ready to send.

When someone responds, Belcoda automatically creates their profile—capturing their phone number, verifying it, and marking them as a WhatsApp subscriber. If they're already in your database, their existing profile is updated and the signup recorded. It's seamless discovery: the system finds people by phone number or creates new profiles as needed, all without manual data entry.

The WhatsApp flow respects consent. People who sign up via WhatsApp are automatically subscribed to WhatsApp communications, reflecting how they've chosen to engage with your community.

### WhatsApp Check-In

For in-person events, generate a separate check-in QR code. Place it at your venue entrance, and attendees can confirm their arrival with a quick scan. Status updates happen instantly in your database, giving you real-time attendance visibility without clipboards or manual roll calls.

### Share Without Friction

Copy WhatsApp links directly from the platform and paste them anywhere: in broadcast messages, group chats, or one-on-one conversations. The links carry all the event context, so recipients understand what they're signing up for before they commit.

