## Event Discovery

### Search and Filter

Find events in your database by title, date, or month. View events on a calendar for visual planning. Filter to see only upcoming events, or include archived events for historical analysis.

Full-text search across event titles helps you locate specific gatherings quickly, even in organizations with dozens of events per month.

### Event Cards

Clean event cards show essential information at a glance: title, date, location, signup count. Cards link to detailed views where you can manage settings, view attendees, or access the public signup page.

