## Technical Foundation

### Real-Time Updates

Belcoda Events uses Rocicorp Zero for real-time data synchronization. When someone signs up, your dashboard updates immediately—no page refresh required. When you update event details, the public page reflects changes within seconds.

### Reliable Email Delivery

Email communications use Postmark for reliable delivery. Messages are templated, branded to your workspace, and localized to recipient languages. Reply-to addresses can be customized per workspace, ensuring responses reach the right organizers.

### Mobile-First Design

Event pages, signup forms, and admin views work beautifully on mobile devices. Most people will access your event page from their phone—the interface is designed for that reality.

---

## Privacy and Consent

Event signups respect individual privacy preferences. People can sign up without receiving automated communications if they're marked "do not contact." Phone numbers and emails are verified through signup channels, establishing clear consent paths.

All event data lives in your community database, not scattered across external platforms. You maintain complete control over who can access attendee information and how it's used.

